text: Tameka Yallop ( Butt; born 16 June 1991) is an Australian soccer player. She plays for Brisbane Roar FC in the Australian A-League Women and for the Australia women's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Matildas"). ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Australian LGBT people Category:Australian women's soccer players Category:LGBT sportspeople Category:Sportspeople from New South Wales
